description:
Sponsored by Mobileye

Autonomous vehicles aren’t just a moonshot—they’re a fast-moving reality. But making them scalable, safe, and city-ready takes more than just machine learning. It takes vision.

This virtual event will take you inside self-driving and the AI-driven evolution of autonomous vehicles. We’ll speak with automotive innovators, AI experts, and urban mobility leaders who are building the blueprint for the future. From advanced driver-assistance systems (ADAS) to city-wide data networks, we’ll explore how the latest breakthroughs in AI and computer vision are turning autonomy into real-world traction.
